<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 21:14:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>FCC主席提出网络安全规则以应对中国盐台风电信黑客攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/fcc-chair-proposes-cybersecurity-rules-response-chinas-salt-typhoon-telecom-hack-2024-12-05/</link><description>美国联邦通信委员会主席杰西卡·罗森沃塞尔 (Jessica Rosenworcel) 在周四的一份声明中表示，该机构提议要求通信服务提供商提交年度认证，证明他们已制定计划来防范网络攻击。该提议部分是为了回应中国所谓的“盐台风”深入美国海域的行为。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 20:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/fcc-chair-proposes-cybersecurity-rules-response-chinas-salt-typhoon-telecom-hack-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>巴拉圭因台湾“干涉”驱逐中国特使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/paraguay-expels-chinese-envoy-over-interference-domestic-affairs-2024-12-05/</link><description>巴拉圭外交部周四表示，巴拉圭以涉嫌“干涉内政”为由取消了中国低级外交官徐伟的签证，并勒令他在24小时内离境。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 19:53:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/paraguay-expels-chinese-envoy-over-interference-domestic-affairs-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>纽约联储分析称，特朗普第一个任期内的关税损害了美国企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/tariffs-under-first-trump-term-hurt-us-firms-ny-fed-analysis-says-2024-12-05/</link><description>美国联邦储备银行(Federal Reserve Bank)的最新分析显示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)第一任期内的进口关税在公布之日就大幅降低了股票价值，并且与股价受到最严重打击的公司的未来利润、销售额和就业率下降有关。纽约工作人员总结道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 17:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/tariffs-under-first-trump-term-hurt-us-firms-ny-fed-analysis-says-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示，风险重新出现在主权和公共基金的菜单上</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/risk-is-back-menu-sovereign-public-funds-survey-shows-2024-12-05/</link><description>官方货币和金融机构论坛的一项调查显示，随着通胀担忧不再是最令人担忧的问题，管理着 6.5 万亿美元的主权和公共基金正在将风险重新纳入考虑范围，并在印度大举押注。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/risk-is-back-menu-sovereign-public-funds-survey-shows-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟海军：中国渔船在索马里海域遭海盗控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/eu-naval-force-chinese-fishing-vessel-under-control-alleged-pirates-somali-2024-12-05/</link><description>欧盟反海盗海军部队周四表示，一艘中国渔船在索马里半自治邦特兰地区的水域被涉嫌海盗控制。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 13:16:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/eu-naval-force-chinese-fishing-vessel-under-control-alleged-pirates-somali-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>日本向菲律宾提供1100万美元安全援助以加强防御</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-grants-philippines-11-mln-security-aid-bolster-defences-2024-12-05/</link><description>日本和菲律宾周四签署了一项价值 16 亿日元（1065 万美元）的安全援助协议，以在南海紧张局势加剧之际提高这个东南亚国家的海上安全和监视能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 12:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-grants-philippines-11-mln-security-aid-bolster-defences-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>习近平强调要在军队中反腐败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-stresses-need-fight-graft-military-2024-12-05/</link><description>据中央电视台周四报道，中国国家主席习近平强调，要加强军队纪律建设、反腐败斗争，并提高信息战能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:58:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-stresses-need-fight-graft-military-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，台积电正在与 Nvidia 就亚利桑那州人工智能芯片生产事宜进行谈判​</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-talks-with-nvidia-ai-chip-production-arizona-sources-say-2024-12-05/</link><description>三名知情人士透露，台积电正在与英伟达公司讨论在该合同制造商位于亚利桑那州的新工厂生产 Blackwell 人工智能芯片。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 09:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-talks-with-nvidia-ai-chip-production-arizona-sources-say-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾就南海事件向中国提出外交抗议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-files-diplomatic-protest-against-china-over-sth-china-sea-incident-2024-12-05/</link><description>菲律宾外交部周四表示，已就12月4日在有争议的南海黄岩岛发生的海上事件向中国提出外交抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 08:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-files-diplomatic-protest-against-china-over-sth-china-sea-incident-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>高管告诉官方媒体，对华为 Mate 70 智能手机的需求“过剩”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/demand-excessive-huaweis-mate-70-smartphones-exec-tells-state-media-2024-12-05/</link><description>华为一位高管周四对国有媒体《证券时报》表示，由于最初准备的供应不足，华为的供应链团队正在加班加点以满足其新款 Mate 70 智能手机的需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/demand-excessive-huaweis-mate-70-smartphones-exec-tells-state-media-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>葛兰素史克从智飞带状疱疹疫苗交易中获得的收益减少；就 RSV 进行合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-expands-deal-with-chinas-zhifei-explore-rsv-vaccine-collaboration-2024-12-05/</link><description>英国制药商周四表示，中国智飞将向葛兰素史克支付约 23 亿英镑（合 29 亿美元），以获得葛兰素史克带状疱疹疫苗在中国的独家经销权，尽管该交易已延期，但该金额低于之前达成的协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-expands-deal-with-chinas-zhifei-explore-rsv-vaccine-collaboration-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>由于担心反倾销税，中国买家大幅削减加拿大油菜籽进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-buyers-slash-canadian-canola-imports-fears-anti-dumping-duty-2024-12-05/</link><description>中国进口商正在减少对加拿大油菜籽的采购，12 月份的发货量可能会大幅下降，因为大多数买家因担心北京可能征收报复性反倾销税而不愿签署新协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-buyers-slash-canadian-canola-imports-fears-anti-dumping-duty-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国化妆品公司毛戈平将在香港首次公开募股中将股票定价定为区间上限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinese-cosmetics-firm-mao-geping-set-price-shares-top-range-hong-hong-ipo-2024-12-05/</link><description>据直接了解情况的消息人士透露，中国化妆品公司毛戈平的股票定价将高于在香港首次公开募股中筹集 2.7 亿美元的价格区间。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 06:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinese-cosmetics-firm-mao-geping-set-price-shares-top-range-hong-hong-ipo-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商转向混合动力汽车以应对欧洲电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-automakers-pivot-hybrids-europe-counter-ev-tariffs-2024-12-05/</link><description>欧盟为保护其汽车工业免受大量廉价中国进口产品的影响而征收的最新电动汽车关税并不适用于混合动力汽车。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 06:43:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-automakers-pivot-hybrids-europe-counter-ev-tariffs-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>香港领导人解雇两名高级官员，旨在“做得更好”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leader-sacks-two-senior-officials-aim-do-better-2024-12-05/</link><description>香港特首李家超周四表示，他出人意料地更换了两名高级官员，他表示此举将最大限度地提高社会和经济效益，并帮助香港“赶上”其他旅游目的地。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:49:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leader-sacks-two-senior-officials-aim-do-better-2024-12-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>